{"tid":1387631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自己MASK自己做。","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T14:46:52.000Z","uid":279840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f6937a4d3a1c845bccb39347705fa0629b2492","tid":1387631,"uid":279840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"簡易防TG面具。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dvlryShN69A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdvlryShN69A&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=f762d629\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dvlryShN69A</a><br />\n<br />\n其實要做防到TEAR GAS既MASK， 唔使幾百買名牌。<br />\n<br />\n講真， 以前D人咪又係咁同防暴打， 好多野唔使買 - 但要學會原理自己DIY。 <br />\n<br />\n唔通政府一要全部五金實名登記就唔使發夢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單D講， 過濾芯你可以用活性碳 （日本城貨大把又平）, 扑碎成粉狀態。用化妝棉包起, 外層包多一層紗布。 成為一個濾芯放番係3M 罩個位頂住先。<br />\n<br />\n係就係冇正板咁耐用， 但係一做做多五六個中場換啦。"},{"pid":"e29544e4d065931311af3bbe7a50ae56e928de71","tid":1387631,"uid":263467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借少少位<br />\n--------------------<br />\n[爸媽系列] 唔可以俾前線得個N95，求裝區。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtjCtT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtjCtT</a>"}]}